quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif, laam, raa: yewtere fii sugu Й—ee Aayeeje yawtiino ka arannde cortewol(simoore) Baqarah. ЖҠee Aayeeje ko mawnuЙ—e fiyaaku, tinndinЙ—e wonnde ko Й—e jippiniaaЙ—e ka Alla, Aayeeje Alqur'aana Й“annginЙ—e tawhiidi e sari'aaji."
  15,2,"HeeferЙ“e Й“en yeloyto Г‘alnde Darngal, tuma feeГұanta Й“e meere keeferaaku ngu Й“e wonunoo e mun aduna, sinno Й“e laatino juulЙ“e."
  15,3,"An NulaaЙ—o, accu Й“ee fennooЙ“e Гұaamira no neemoraaЙ—i Гұaamirta, Й“e dakmitora dakamme aduna lannayЙ—e, Й“e sokolira juutingol caate gaa gomЙ—inal e golle moЖҙЖҙe. Aray Й“e annda ko Й“e wonunoo e hayrere kon, tuma Й“e darnoyaa yeeso Alla Г‘alnde Darngal."
  15,4,"Men jippinaali halkaare e saare jeyaande e tooГұunde, si wanaa hara no woodani nde lajal dot-tangal anndaangal ka Alla, ngal Й“eydotaako ngal Й—uytotaako."
  15,5,"Mofte woo halketaake ado lajal majje timmude, Й—e nennantaake Й—um kadi si hewtii. Haani hara tooГұooЙ“e Й“en Й—aynitoraali ko Alla nennitirani Й“e kon."
  15,6,"HeeferЙ“e makka Й“en wi'ani NulaaЙ—o Alla on (yo o his): Ko an yo nodditiiЙ—o jippineede e mun (Deftere nden), pellet aan e noddugol maa ko a kaangaaЙ—o haЙ—a firlito pirlitagol feetuЙ—o."
  15,7,"Ko haЙ— Ma addande amen Malaykaaji Й—i ceedo wonde ko a goonЙ—uЙ—o e nelal ma he e tellagol lepte."
  15,8,"Alla jaaborii Жҙamol maЙ“Й“e addugol Malaa'ika ngol: Men jippinirtaa Malaa'ika si wanaa ko yahdata e ГұeenГұal, tuma hewti halkirgol Й“e lepte. ЖҒe wonoy- tah, tuma Men addoyta Malaa'ika, hara Й“e gomЙ—i- naali, leelnoyteeЙ“e, ko woni, Й“e yacciniroyte lepte Й—en."
  15,9,"Ko Menen woni ko jippini ndee Alqur'aanaare e fonndo Muhammadu (jom-kisiyee) siftinore yimЙ“e Й“en. Menen kadi ko Men reenooЙ“e nde e Й“eydee- de maa Й—uyteede, maa walylee, waЙ—titee."
  15,10,"GomЙ—ii Men nuliino ado maa an NulaaЙ—o, NulaaЙ“e goo, e leГұi yeddunooЙ“e ko adii, Й“e fenni Й“e. Wanaa an adaa fenneede e NulaaЙ“e Й“en."
  15,11,"NulaaЙ—o woo araali e Й—en mofte heeferЙ“e adinooЙ“e, si wanaa Й“e fennay mo Й“e jalkita."
  15,12,"Ko wano Men naadirnoo fennugol ngol e Й“erЙ—e Й—en mofte, Men naadirta Й—um e Й“erЙ—e sirkooЙ“e Makka Й“en, sabu Й—uurnagol Й“e townitoo ngol."
  15,13,"ЖҒe gomЙ—intaa ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo o his), gomЙ—ii sunna Alla on e halkugol fennuЙ“e NulaaЙ“e mun Й“en yawtiino. Yo fennooЙ“e ma Й“en waajito."
  15,14,"ЖҒee fennooЙ“e townitiiЙ“e, hay goonga kan feeГұirani Й“e hujjaaji Й“annguЙ—i, hay Men udditanno Й“e damal ka kammu, Й“e waЙ—ti Жҙawrude."
  15,15,"ЖҒe goongintaano, Й“e wi'ayno : Anndee gite amen Й—en hippa e yi'ugol. Wurin ko men yi'aynoo ko batte mbilewu, ko men mbilaa Й“e."